1944 2456 the ship of fools reached cruising speed on friday evening , when we had the frightening scene of republicans so crazed with hatred of the president that they were railroading through an impeachment even though the united states was at war with iraq , even though the house chamber was mostly empty , even though republicans were huddled in a glass house on the issue of sex and lies , and even though the white house was still pitching a tent and planning sleigh rides for a winter wonderland press party on monday. < mention mentionid= '' 105